{"tid":359002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍25歲女手機App交友被姦    重案組拉色魔","createTime":"2017-08-14T06:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T11:26:25.000Z","uid":48093,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"add67009bf09696ebc0b5966c10377e078ab4044","tid":359002,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170814/large/1502654312_1b52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170814%2Flarge%2F1502654312_1b52.jpg&h=8a796583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【14:17更新】重案組今晨在天水圍拘捕涉強姦的29歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n一名25歲女子早前結識一名中國籍男子後，昨日於天水圍天瑞路一單位懷疑被他強姦，於是在晚上7時許報警。她被送往屯門醫院查。涉案色魔年約20歲，蓄黑短髮，中等身材，案件暫列強姦，交元朗警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，女事主無業，早前透過手機App交友網，認識姓林（29歲）男子，兩人其後在WeChat 聊天傾談，直至昨晚，女事主應邀到林位於天恩邨的寓所，其間有人露出狼相，女事主慘遭對方強姦，她受辱後向住在天水圍的友人訴苦，並報警求助。元朗重案組接手案件後，今晨掩至林的寓所，將他拘捕帶署續查。"},{"pid":"484be8a067bf90dc5c52915903ae6e5ab790528c","tid":359002,"uid":50745,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"到底係20定29"},{"pid":"9915c903445889e7eaeb88ffcb6111a0f37ab2c9","tid":359002,"uid":11148,"like":21,"dislike":12,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"勞資糾紛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afec598606a8fb51a7160693a36d5fe7964059af","tid":359002,"uid":11148,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底係20定29</blockquote><br />\n香港記者就快追上台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80d6808aecb04483798506a06902238357853fe","tid":359002,"uid":63909,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"好人好姐用WE7識人<br />\n仲去人屋企<br />\n仲成25歲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1029c4a819ef884a2d9d4dfdfcdd1ba4ca4d6a","tid":359002,"uid