smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哦, 居屋正呀! 夠實用.<br />\n行咁過去中.................<br />\n女: 咦. 呢道咪天頌苑囉? 邊道係你屋企?<br />\n男: 係呀. 就到架喇. 過埋條天橋...<br />\n女: (心諗: 仆街. 天恩村? 公屋黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 咦. 呢道係天恩村喎?<br />\n男: 係呀! 我咪住天恩村囉. 柏慧豪庭,天頌苑個頭丫嘛.............<br />\n女: (屌......上佢屋企屙完篤尿就走先...........)"},{"pid":"74c81446c70acc8d94a265d4248581333e6ac7b4","tid":359002,"uid":53586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底係20定29</blockquote>"},{"pid":"68116c213819860fe6995a38c3ab60a08c2448ab","tid":359002,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>色魔會唔會又吊頸自殺</blockquote><br />\n大陸人無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769e276c52dad78c0a4887b3294c8f9c4274b31a","tid":359002,"uid":24160,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:07:27.000Z","msg":"又係姓林??<br />\n九龍灣, 屯門寶田, 天順邨<br />\n都係姓林<br />\n<br />\n姓林係咪變態啲?"},{"pid":"20ee3298ee25ec94c1946ad1f45b85b6af694250","tid":359002,"uid":129882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>到底係20定29</blockquote><br />\n識咗個29歲 之後俾個20歲嘅人強姦</blockquote><br />\n年約20歲<br />\n但實際29歲</blockquote><br />\n20歲係錄口供時估計<br />\n29歲係拉咗之後證實"},{"pid":"d0d6c2e083b00a40e35f4ce66efff85d144fc76c","tid":359002,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:45:46.000Z","msg":"係自己屋企落手,要幾撚蠢既人先做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d垃圾直接啪左佢就岩,唔好晒米飯養"},{"pid":"e2e15d2e5e9027e936c0bda03ff53fec95a93e07","tid":359002,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8d8069564a47ba89fa2c64fb4a6f6d29886e8ba","tid":359002,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:57:47.000Z","msg